The ExtRATerrestrial is a visitor to our planet from far away. Although we do not know if its initial intentions were to befriend us or do us harm, it has fallen under the spell of pizza and now calls our little planet home.

This rat was created by Brokenthumbs as a reward for winning our first ever rat race!

570.description:

This rat was created by DancesWithBulls as a reward for winning our first ever rat race!
